room_title: Escape room "The Doll Master" by Escape SBC in Shreveport
room_description: He creates a doll before he kills them.  Then, sends the doll to the family as something to remember them by.  But HER doll never got sent.  Can you find a way to rescue her doll and get it to her family before The Doll Master returns and YOUR doll is the one that will need to be set free?
